data.description: This beautiful 1 story Hill Country home is located in a gated neighborhood with Medina Lake access and a park. The house sits on a flat 5 acre lot with many mature trees which tucks the home away from the road. Wonderful open floor plan, stone fireplace, high ceilings with beams, plenty of natural light, and also a new water softener system. The kitchen features a down draft smooth cooktop and large breakfast bar which opens into the living room. Outside has a large deck for entertaining, fire pit, and a large storage shed.
